{"tid":1511534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"職工盟明愛丁堡廣場集會 獲警方發不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T04:25:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bcfc24fae1b1983b6eee72dfb904b1098bf2c38a","tid":1511534,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"職工盟今日（27日）晚上表示，明日（28日）下午4至7時於中環受丁堡廣場舉行集會，再遊行至太古廣場，表達停止白色恐怖、撤回解僱決定、捍衛言論自由等訴求，集會已獲警方發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟原定周三（28日）於國泰城舉行集會，昨晚遭警方正式發出反對通知書，職工盟今日就此提出上訴，最後亦被駁回。職工盟主席吳敏兒對上訴結果感失望，批評警方剥削集會自由，又認為委員會的決定是令集會權利收到最窄，有偏幫僱主之嫌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qePThLO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqePThLO.png&h=b2a817c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0506ba98f85ccf18c8fec26c97ce242ba63c0e8","tid":1511534,"uid":59225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=44e1ee51\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=2de1bbfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=dae15638\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"e44b033dde611fc8d37d1e035a2d8c59a65819eb","tid":1511534,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":